## Tests

```bash
pytest tests/ -v
```

Test configuration: `pytest.ini` sets `asyncio_mode = auto` (no `@pytest.mark.asyncio` decorator needed).

**Note:** No test coverage exists for `ideation.py`, `builder.py`, `deep_research.py`, or `competitor_intel.py`.
